---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Nathan Kisiel';
---

<BaseLayout {pageTitle}>
  <!-- HOME -->
  <section id="home" class="home-hero">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h1 class="home-hero__title">Nathan Kisiel</h1>

      <p class="home-hero__blurb">
        Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin feugiat porta nulla,
        quis vehicula nisi porttitor eget. Fusce eget vehicula nisl, at molestie magna.
        Morbi lacinia dui eget libero placerat semper.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT -->
  <section id="about" class="about">
    <div class="section-inner about__inner">
      <h2 class="about__title">About Me</h2>

      <div class="about__image-wrap">
        <img
          class="about__image"
          src="/img/about pic.png"
          alt="Abstract mountains illustration"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="about__text">
        <p>
          I’m a rising senior at Allegheny College pursuing a B.S. in Mathematics with a focus on actuarial science. 
          I’m actively preparing for actuarial certification while completing my undergraduate studies and have successfully 
          passed the Society of Actuaries Exam P and Exam FM.
        </p>

        <p>
          My academic interests center on probability, financial mathematics, and risk modeling, and I enjoy applying quantitative theory to real-world financial and insurance problems. 
          Through coursework and independent projects, I’ve developed a strong foundation in analytical thinking, problem-solving, and mathematical modeling.
        </p>

        <p>
          I’m currently seeking opportunities to apply my skills in an actuarial or analytical role where I can 
          continue learning, contribute meaningfully, and grow within the profession.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ACTUARY EXAMS -->
<section id="exams" class="exams">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 class="exams__title">Actuary Exams</h2>

    <div class="exams__grid">
      <!-- Exam P -->
      <article class="exam-card">
        <div class="exam-card__top">
          <h3 class="exam-card__title">Exam P — Probability</h3>
          <span class="exam-card__status exam-card__status--passed">Passed</span>
        </div>

        <p class="exam-card__text">
          Through Exam P, I developed a strong foundation in probability theory and its application to modeling uncertainty. I learned how to work with discrete and continuous random variables, common probability distributions, and key measures such as expected value, variance, and covariance. The exam also strengthened my understanding of conditional probability, Bayes’ theorem, and joint distributions, which helped me see how multiple sources of risk can interact within a single model.
        </p>

        <div class="exam-tags">
          <span class="exam-tag">Probability Theory</span>
          <span class="exam-tag">Statistical Modeling</span>
          <span class="exam-tag">Quantitative Analysis</span>
          <span class="exam-tag">Expected Value & Variance Analysis</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Exam FM -->
      <article class="exam-card">
        <div class="exam-card__top">
          <h3 class="exam-card__title">Exam FM — Financial Mathematics</h3>
          <span class="exam-card__status exam-card__status--passed">Passed</span>
        </div>

        <p class="exam-card__text">
          Exam FM taught me the core principles of financial mathematics and the time value of money. I gained experience calculating present and future values of cash flows and working with annuities, loans, amortization schedules, and bonds. I also learned how interest rates and compounding affect long-term financial obligations and how to evaluate cash flows using yield rates.
        </p>

        <div class="exam-tags">
          <span class="exam-tag">Interest Theory</span>
          <span class="exam-tag">Duration & Convexity</span>
          <span class="exam-tag">Financial Modeling</span>
          <span class="exam-tag">Bond Pricing & Yield Analysis</span>
          <span class="exam-tag">Risk & Return Concepts</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Exam SRM -->
      <article class="exam-card">
        <div class="exam-card__top">
          <h3 class="exam-card__title">Exam SRM — Statistics for Risk Modeling</h3>
          <span class="exam-card__status exam-card__status--progress">In Progress</span>
        </div>

        <p class="exam-card__text">
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Proin feugiat porta nulla,
          quis vehicula nisi porttitor eget. Fusce eget vehicula nisl, at molestie magna. 
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque faucibus ex sapien vitae pellentesque sem placerat.
        </p>

        <div class="exam-tags">
          <span class="exam-tag">Lorem Ipsum</span>
